Perform imposition of a PDF file.

Imposition consists in the arrangement of the printed product’s pages on the
printer’s sheet, in order to obtain faster printing, simplify binding and
reduce paper waste (source: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Imposition).

Install
=======

You can run the program without installing it using `bin/pdfimpose`. To
install it, run:

  python3 setup.py install

Documentation
=============

You can build the documentation using:

  cd doc && make html
